{"type":"message","id":"61937d72","parentId":"e7c79f6e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:35:11.843Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qi2hbs1b7qgg_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 143341\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: a (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and what needs to be done next.\r\n\r\nLooking at the goals:\r\n1. Phase 0 COMPLETE - Sandbox foundation established\r\n2. Phase 1 COMPLETE - Architecture cross-analysis + integration spec synthesized\r\n\r\nKey findings from this session:\r\n- CFI compression experiment ran successfully\r\n- Found that CFI ≥ 0.7 AND freq < 60 is TOO aggressive\r\n- Discovered \"Constant Format Problem\" - tokens like \"for next instantiation\", \"pulse\", \"completed at:\" with freq=160, CFI=1.00 are metaprogramming artifacts\r\n- \"Phase 1\" (freq=136, CFI=0.96) is true research trajectory\r\n\r\nThe pending experiment is:\r\n- Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n- Formula: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n- Need to test if this distinguishes \"constant format\" from \"research trajectory\"\r\n\r\nI should implement the hybrid scoring experiment as the next concrete action. Let me look at what files exist and what needs to be created.\r\n\r\nFrom the research, there's:\r\n- research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md - the full experiment results\r\n- Need to create a new experiment script for Strategy C (hybrid scoring)\r\n\r\nLet me create the hybrid scoring experiment. I'll need to:\r\n1. Create a script that computes score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n2. Compare against binary thresholds\r\n3. Run on the same 200 pulses with 80/20 split\r\n\r\nLet me look at what exists. I should check if there's existing code I can reference from the CFI experiment.\r\n\r\nActually, I should focus on the next concrete action. The pending experiment is to run the hybrid CFI×Freq scoring. Let me create the experiment script.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI compression synthesis identified the \"Constant Format Problem\" - tokens with freq=160 and CFI=1.00 are metaprogramming artifacts that look causal but have zero information content. The hybrid scoring formula score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120) should theoretically distinguish these from true research trajectory tokens.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate Strategy C hybrid scoring experiment script to test whether CFI × min(1, freq/120) outperforms binary CFI thresholds at identifying tokens with genuine information content (distinguishing \"for next instantiation\" from \"Phase 1\").\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Strategy C: Hybrid CFI×Freq^0.5 Scoring Experiment\r\n# Hypothesis: score(T) = CFI(T) × sqrt(min(1, freq(T)/120))\r\n# This penalizes constant-format tokens (freq=160) while rewarding research tokens (freq<120)\r\n# \r\n# Test: Does this distinguish \"constant format\" (freq≈160, CFI=1) from \"research trajectory\" (freq<120, CFI>0.5)?\r\n# Run: 200 pulses, 80/20 split, compare against binary thresholds\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$SampleSize = 200,\r\n    [float]$TrainSplit = 0.8,\r\n    [string]$PulseDir = \"pulses\",\r\n    [string]$OutputFile = \"research/STRATEGY_C_RESULTS.md\"\r\n)\r\n\r\n# ===== TOKEN EXTRACTION =====\r\nfunction Get-TokenMetrics {\r\n    param([string[]]$Lines)\r\n    \r\n    $tokenCounts = @{}\r\n    $pulseCount = 0\r\n    $currentPulseTokens = @{}\r\n    \r\n    foreach ($line in $Lines) {\r\n        # Detect new pulse boundary\r\n        if ($line -match \"^pulse_(\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2})_(\\d{6})\\.md\") {\r\n            if ($currentPulseTokens.Count -gt 0) {\r\n                foreach ($tok in $currentPulseTokens.Keys) {\r\n                    $tokenCounts[$tok]++\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            $currentPulseTokens = @{}\r\n            $pulseCount++\r\n        }\r\n        \r\n        # Extract tokens (simplified: words and short sequences)\r\n        $tokens = [regex]::Matches($line, '\\b\\w+\\b') | ForEach-Object { $_.Value }\r\n        foreach ($tok in $tokens) {\r\n            if (-not $currentPulseTokens.ContainsKey($tok)) {\r\n                $currentPulseTokens[$tok] = $true\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Don't forget last pulse\r\n    if ($currentPulseTokens.Count -gt 0) {\r\n        foreach ($tok in $currentPulseTokens.Keys) {\r\n            if (-not $tokenCounts.ContainsKey($tok)) {\r\n                $tokenCounts[$tok] = 1\r\n            } else {\r\n                $tokenCounts[$tok]++\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        $pulseCount++\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return @{\r\n        TokenCounts = $tokenCounts\r\n        TotalPulses = $pulseCount\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# ===== CFI COMPUTATION =====\r\nfunction Get-CFI {\r\n    param($TokenCounts, $TotalPulses)\r\n    \r\n    $cfiData = @{}\r\n    foreach ($token in $TokenCounts.Keys) {\r\n        $freq = $TokenCounts[$token]\r\n        $cfi = $freq / $TotalPulses\r\n        $cfiData[$token] = @{\r\n            Frequency = $freq\r\n            CFI = $cfi\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    return $cfiData\r\n}\r\n\r\n# ===== STRATEGY C SCORING =====\r\nfunction Get-HybridScore {\r\n    param([float]$CFI, [int]$Freq, [int]$TotalPulses)\r\n    \r\n    # Normalized frequency: capped at 120\r\n    $normFreq = [\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 14:34:02\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774377311837}}
